00:40:22,485 --> 00:40:23,417
And butterfly.

552
00:40:33,596 --> 00:40:35,029
Where are you going?

553
00:40:35,097 --> 00:40:36,029
What?

554
00:40:38,601 --> 00:40:40,034
Where are you going?

555
00:40:40,102 --> 00:40:42,036
I thought I'd go downstairs.

556
00:40:42,104 --> 00:40:44,038
Do some work for tomorrow.

557
00:40:44,106 --> 00:40:47,041
You had a full day today, didn't you?

558
00:40:47,109 --> 00:40:48,542
Yes, I certainly did.

559
00:40:48,611 --> 00:40:51,045
You still got some energy left?

560
00:40:51,113 --> 00:40:52,546
Oh, lot of work.

