568
00:41:22,578 --> 00:41:24,068
Midwest Cab, Jollytime Playthings...

569
00:41:24,146 --> 00:41:25,113
Jollytime Playthings?

570
00:41:25,180 --> 00:41:26,579
Yes, Jollytime Playthings.

571
00:41:26,649 --> 00:41:30,176
Remind me to get a present for my daughter.

572
00:41:30,252 --> 00:41:31,617
Bahamas Ship-to-Shore...

573
00:41:31,687 --> 00:41:33,120
The list is endless.

574
00:41:33,188 --> 00:41:35,053
