the Capone organization.

685
00:48:09,965 --> 00:48:11,398
He'll bring with him

686
00:48:11,467 --> 00:48:14,402
full payment for the shipment in cash.

687
00:48:14,470 --> 00:48:17,837
The meet is to occur just over the border,

688
00:48:17,907 --> 00:48:19,374
on the American side.

689
00:48:19,441 --> 00:48:23,309
Our aim is to confiscate the liquor and the cash.

690
00:48:23,379 --> 00:48:24,937
Captain.

691
00:48:25,014 --> 00:48:27,312
We will await their signal.

692
00:48:27,383 --> 00:48:29,817
When they are on the road

693
00:48:29,885 --> 00:48:31,819
and have given the signal,

694
00:48:31,887 --> 00:48:35,323
