00:49:39,655 --> 00:49:40,815
Yes, sir,

713
00:49:40,889 --> 00:49:42,322
that I am.

714
00:49:45,294 --> 00:49:47,228
Did you check it already?

715
00:49:47,296 --> 00:49:48,729
Yes, I did.

716
00:49:48,797 --> 00:49:50,526
Then leave it alone.

717
00:49:50,599 --> 00:49:53,727
You're a good cop, Giuseppe.

718
00:49:53,802 --> 00:49:56,737
You're doing good.
You're going to do just fine.

719
00:49:59,908 --> 00:50:01,842
Now, Wallace, are you cold?

720
00:50:01,910 --> 00:50:02,842
Mm.

721
00:50:02,911 --> 00:50:04,845
Yes, I am a little.

722
00:50:04,913 --> 00:50:06,346
Then stamp your feet.

723
00:50:06,415 --> 00:50:07,848
It'll keep you warm.

724
00:50:07,916 --> 00:50:10,851
You learn something 20 years walking a beat.

