00:50:12,921 --> 00:50:14,513
standing in the rain.

728
00:50:14,590 --> 00:50:17,525
[Stamps Feet]

729
00:50:44,319 --> 00:50:46,412
Listen, Mr. Ness.

730
00:50:46,488 --> 00:50:48,285
Mm-hmm?

731
00:50:48,357 --> 00:50:50,382
I had an idea.

732
00:50:50,459 --> 00:50:51,824
Shh. Shh.

733
00:51:44,413 --> 00:51:47,348
You all have your spare shells, huh?

734
00:52:02,931 --> 00:52:05,399
If you have to fire,

735
00:52:05,467 --> 00:52:07,958
