737
00:52:13,142 --> 00:52:15,804
'Cause he'd do the same to you.

738
00:52:15,878 --> 00:52:17,436
Shoot to kill.

739
00:52:17,513 --> 00:52:19,674
You hear what I said?

740
00:52:19,748 --> 00:52:22,182
Yes, I did.
Shoot to kill.

741
00:52:24,386 --> 00:52:25,853
Let's go.

742
00:52:49,444 --> 00:52:50,570
[Neigh]

743
00:52:50,646 --> 00:52:52,204
Easy.

744
00:52:52,281 --> 00:52:55,808
The Canadians won't show
until I flash the badge.

745
00:52:55,884 --> 00:52:59,843
It's imperative we cross
from here to the bridge quickly.

746
00:52:59,922 --> 00:53:01,321
George, the count's right.

747
00:53:01,390 --> 00:53:02,823
That doesn't concern me.

748
00:53:02,891 --> 00:53:05,257
The size of these barrels concerns me.

749
00:53:05,327 --> 00:53:06,351
Malone, we'll...

