756
00:53:24,313 --> 00:53:25,337
Look!

757
00:53:25,414 --> 00:53:27,439
It's the Mounties!

758
00:53:27,516 --> 00:53:29,450
Let's get out of here!

759
00:53:29,518 --> 00:53:30,746
The booze!

760
00:53:40,362 --> 00:53:41,294
Let's go!

761
00:53:41,363 --> 00:53:42,796
Behind you.
Cover us.

762
00:53:47,069 --> 00:53:48,366
I can't believe it.

763
00:53:48,437 --> 00:53:49,870
Here. The book.

764
00:53:49,938 --> 00:53:51,701
Give me.
To the car.

765
00:53:51,773 --> 00:53:54,571
Don't let those cars off the bridge!

766
00:54:01,984 --> 00:54:03,042
Ha ha!

767
00:54:03,118 --> 00:54:04,050
Whoo!

768
00:54:12,461 --> 00:54:14,292
Stone, take the first car.

769
00:54:37,853 --> 00:54:39,480
Tough guy.

770
00:54:42,591 --> 00:54:44,491
Stone!

771
00:54:44,559 --> 00:54:45,491
Go!

772
00:54:47,796 --> 00:54:48,728
Stone!

773
00:54:50,666 --> 00:54:52,133
I'm O.K.

774
00:54:53,335 --> 00:54:54,734
You bas...

