00:55:11,987 --> 00:55:13,511
Yeah.

777
00:55:13,588 --> 00:55:16,733
There he is.
Go get him!

778
00:55:27,110 --> 00:55:28,042
[Gunfire]

779
00:55:28,111 --> 00:55:29,271
All right.

780
00:55:29,346 --> 00:55:31,473
Enough of this running.

781
00:55:31,548 --> 00:55:32,981
Well, Georgie boy.

782
00:55:33,050 --> 00:55:36,349
Well, what have we got here?

783
00:55:36,420 --> 00:55:38,012
Hello.

784
00:55:38,088 --> 00:55:39,020
Huh?

785
00:55:40,624 --> 00:55:42,421
Yaa!

786
00:55:44,127 --> 00:55:45,059
Yaa!

787
00:55:48,865 --> 00:55:50,264
Yaa!

788
00:55:51,968 --> 00:55:52,900
[Click]

789
00:55:56,673 --> 00:56:01,975
Yaa!

790
00:56:20,464 --> 00:56:21,396
Ah.

791
00:56:57,367 --> 00:56:58,959
[Speaking ltalian]

792
00:57:00,404 --> 00:57:02,736
All right!
Drop the gun!

793
00:57:02,806 --> 00:57:06,367
Put your hands in the air.
You're under arrest.

794
00:57:06,443 --> 00:57:07,933
I said drop it!

795
00:57:09,579 --> 00:57:10,978
[Speaking Italian]

796
00:57:13,617 --> 00:57:14,606
Ah...

797
00:57:16,119 --> 00:57:19,054
