803
00:58:04,801 --> 00:58:07,736
I got the fella with the satchel.

804
00:58:14,678 --> 00:58:16,407
I had to kill him.

805
00:58:16,480 --> 00:58:19,415
Oh, yeah. He's as dead as Julius Caesar.

806
00:58:21,351 --> 00:58:23,785
Would you rather it was you?

807
00:58:23,854 --> 00:58:25,287
No, I would not.

808
00:58:25,355 --> 00:58:27,220
Then you've done your duty.

809
00:58:27,290 --> 00:58:29,724
Go home and sleep well tonight.

810
00:58:29,793 --> 00:58:33,729
The things you see when
you're out without your gun.

811
00:58:33,797 --> 00:58:37,233
You're a long way from the South Side, George.

812
00:58:37,300 --> 00:58:38,733
I'm talking to you.

813
00:58:38,802 --> 00:58:41,737
Did you come here to open a shooting gallery?

814
00:58:41,805 --> 00:58:45,741
Write down the names of your
superiors and your contacts.

815
00:58:45,809 --> 00:58:47,242
